  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いや〜獣化はさすがに無理だけど
リバースならそんな事言われないっしょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah weeell, dealing with  the half beastie
was no good, but I bet it won't be like that
for Rebirth.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>すごいよなぁ、ゼロス。
こんだけ失敗してもまだ諦めないなんて</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're awesome, Zelos.
Even with all these losses,
you still won't call it quits.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そりゃそうよ。
モテたいっていう気持ちは
すべてのものに勝っちゃうものよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well of course.
The need to be popular rises above all else.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
